        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Lee\\'s mission log, volume 28.1... I\\'m carrying out an operation on my own. This footage is for my personal use only. Refer to Gray Raven\\'s mission report for actual details.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Greenwich Mean Time 07:07. These mechanoid guards are all lined up facing the \"golden light beam.\" They are... saluting something.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'The objective of this solo operation was to search for my missing teammate Liv. Now, however, I\\'m stuck here...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Although they\\'re not moving, I have detected a \"current web\" in the air. Based on my analysis, half a step out there is enough for the mild current to catch my whereabouts...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Whoever designed this \"current web\" knows that salutation is when the defense of this area is at its most vulnerable. That\\'s why...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Lee', 3: 'I can only lie here... As long as they don\\'t move, I can\\'t move either.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
